在2013年[[互动艺术与科学学会|互动艺术与科学学会]]评出的D.I.C.E.互动成就奖中，《孤岛惊魂3》被提名七个奖项，包括“年度最佳游戏”、“年度最佳动作游戏”、“动画杰出成就”、“艺术杰出成就”、“原创音乐杰出成就”、“游戏杰出成就”以及“杰出人物表现”。<ref name="2013Dice">{{cite web |first= |last= |url=http://www.interactive.org/images/awards/16th-Annual-D.I.C.E.-Finalists-For-Web.pdf |title=Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences - 16th Annual D.I.C.E. Awards Finalists |publisher=[[Academy_of_Interactive_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences]] |work= |date=2013-01-14 |accessdate=2013-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ECAL7w6s?url=http://www.interactive.org/images/awards/16th-Annual-D.I.C.E.-Finalists-For-Web.pdf |archivedate=2013-02-05 |deadurl=no |format=PDF }}</ref>

本作还受到了两项[[游戏开发者选择奖|游戏开发者选择奖]]提名的最佳视觉艺术和最佳技术奖<ref name="2013GDC">{{cite web |first=Evan |last=Narcisse |url=http://kotaku.com/5978790/here-are-the-2012-games-that-game-developers-want-to-give-awards-to |title=Here Are the 2012 Games That Developers Want to Give Awards to |publisher=Gawker Media |work=Kotaku |date=2013-01-24 |accessdate=2013-01-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DvA2Wlaq?url=http://kotaku.com/5978790/here-are-the-2012-games-that-game-developers-want-to-give-awards-to |archivedate=2013-01-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外，在第九届英国学术游戏奖中，游戏获得了最佳游戏，最佳艺术成就，最佳音乐成就，最佳游戏设计和剧情的提名，并获得了最佳动作游戏奖<ref name="2013BATFAgames">{{cite web |first= |last= |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a463490/bafta-games-awards-2013-winners-in-full.html |title=BAFTA Games Awards 2013 Winners In Full |publisher=Digital Spy |work= |date=2013-03-05 |accessdate=2013-03-10 |archive-date=2013-11-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6LRsiDTVy?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a463490/bafta-games-awards-2013-winners-in-full.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
